{
  "id": "62fb5d8f0cd8b60023b00632",
  "title": "エバーグリーンノート",
  "created": 1660640658,
  "updated": 1780859437,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62fb5d8f0cd8b60023b00632",
      "text": "エバーグリーンノート",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1660640658,
      "updated": 1660640658
    },
    {
      "id": "62fb5d925b98c200007c6565",
      "text": " [いつまでも使えるノート]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1660640659,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1ba",
      "text": " 　[Andy Matuschak]（[誰？]）氏が[発案]した[ノート戦略]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1bb",
      "text": " 　[時間の経過と共に進化しながら蓄積される]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1bc",
      "text": "  [他のノートと密接にリンクする]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1bd",
      "text": "  [APIのようなタイトルをつける]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1be",
      "text": "  [再利用しやすい]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1bf",
      "text": "  [常に保守をし続ける]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1c0",
      "text": " [ノートを大事に育てていく]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1c1",
      "text": "  [Evernote]への[アンチテーゼ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1c2",
      "text": "   [アウトライン]を作って、[既存]の[アトミックノート]の[活用方法]を[検討する]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1c3",
      "text": "   [小さなMOCを作る]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1780859437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1c4",
      "text": " [十分に育ったノート]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1c5",
      "text": " [evergreen notes]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
    {
      "id": "69f609c10000000000bae1c6",
      "text": " [英語圏]では「[🌱Evergreen note]」っていう感じで、よく[絵文字]付きで書かれてる（[らしい]）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777732033,
      "updated": 1777732033
    },
